I sometimes i think &quot;if this was the last day of my life what would i do , who would i spend it with&quot;
And it&#x27;s all about love , I&#x27;d spend it with my family and gf , and maybe write some code or some silly app for the last time.
It&#x27;s important that we keep in mind that life isn&#x27;t a limitless resource ,  and &quot;nobody will remember your ppt presentations when you&#x27;re gone&quot;
